	this resulted in sed errors in config.status. Reported by Worlfgang
	Erlenkoetter. Thanks.
	* configure.in: a hyphen is not allowed for the "Version" section in
	a spec file.
	* .cvsignore: add .orig and .rej.
	* pam_mysql.spec.in: require OpenSSL by default.

